room_title: Escape room "Last Resort" by Panic Room CT in Stamford
room_description: You and your friends are in town and are looking for somewhere to stay the night. The only local establishment with rooms available is the secluded Last Resort hotel. When no one is available to check you in, things start to unravel, proving this small hotel may not be as innocent as it seems. Do you have what it takes to survive the next chapter in the Cryptex Killer saga?
